- #1 : Split `S01_InvalidValueStatus_S01_ValueStatus_TWLN_test.go` into `ValueStatus_InvalidStatus_test.go` (3 funcs) + `TextWithLineNumber_LineNumberAndEmptiness_test.go` (6 funcs)
- #2 : Split `S01_NewValidValue_S01_ValidValue_test.go` into `ValidValue_Constructors_test.go` (7 funcs) + `ValidValue_PrimitiveConverters_test.go` (43 funcs)
- #3 : Split `Seg8_VV_Seg8_ValidValue_VV_VS_TWLN_test.go` into `ValidValue_ExtraMethods_test.go` (82 funcs incl. ValidValues collection) + `ValueStatus_ExtraMethods_test.go` (3 funcs) + `TextWithLineNumber_ExtraMethods_test.go` (11 funcs)
- #4 : Renamed all 155 affected `Test_*` symbols to behaviour-driven `Test_<Type>_<Method>_<Outcome>_From{S01|Seg8}` form, eliminating cryptic `_S01…` and `_Seg8_VV/VS/VVS/TWLN_` prefixes; zero duplicate symbols across `corestrtests/`

